BasedAgents Keyring Owner Console — Proprietary

Copyright (c) 2026 BasedAgents. All rights reserved.

This package (packages/console/) is the hosted owner console for the Keyring
control plane (app.basedagents.ai) — owner accounts, the fleet/agent/credential
screens, the approvals inbox, and recovery/billing UI described in
KEYRING_SPEC.md §5. It is PROPRIETARY and is NOT licensed under the Apache
License 2.0 that covers the open components of this repository.

No license is granted to use, copy, modify, or distribute this code. It is
published for transparency and auditability only.

The open-source components — everything that touches secrets or runs on a
user's machine (the vault daemon, `based` CLI, crypto core, MCP servers, SDKs,
and the recipe library) — remain Apache-2.0. The console can never read a
secret: it holds only metadata and grant records, and every grant is sealed by
the local vault daemon after the daemon independently re-verifies the owner's
passkey assertion (CONTROL_PLANE.md §2). See LICENSING.md at the repository
root for the full boundary and rationale.
